{"tid":1847723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主黨南區黨團：嚴控武漢肺炎 立即全封口岸","createTime":"2020-01-28T07:30:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T08:03:43.000Z","uid":70063,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1aeebb67e057b254ca5b8a4e72a3a46914a07b96","tid":1847723,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:30:22.000Z","msg":"鑒於武漢肺炎開始在本港蔓延，民主派議員昨日(1月27日) 遊行至禮賓府，要求香港政府封閉所有通往內地的口岸。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨南區黨團認為，香港政府對疫症在社區爆發責無旁貸。由署理行政長官張建宗到林鄭月娥的處理方法都令大眾嘩然，防疫政策對比周邊地區執行極度遲緩，錯失多個關鍵時刻。<br />\n<br />\n我們嚴正要求，香港政府必須盡快關閉所有通往內地的口岸，暫時禁止所有內地人來港。與此同時，放棄使用粉嶺暉明苑作為隔離營，重新考慮將解放軍軍營作為隔離營使用，並確保社區口罩穩定供應，防止任何囤積居奇或趁火打劫的事出現。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨南區黨團<br />\n羅健熙 徐遠華 嚴駿豪 黎熙琳<br />\n陳欣兒 陳炳洋 潘秉康 陳堡明<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/YimC.Philip/posts/474520993232975\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FYimC.Philip%2Fposts%2F474520993232975&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb3Qc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=1a4bcfbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/YimC.Philip/posts/474520993232975</a>"},{"pid":"b27c844cbdb3d79838011ddce5f09fd179532cf5","tid":1847723,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:32:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">除咗醫護之外<br />\n垃圾政府都推緊社福界去死</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">學校停 政府部門停 康文設施都停<br />\n啲人就湧晒去唔停嘅中心<br />\n社區爆發岌岌可危<br />\n<br />\n<ins>要求立即停止所有非緊急服務</ins></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845195\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845195</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AS4YPwC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAS4YPwC.jpg&h=a350fa60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb0b6091ca6ca9af460ad326891b2f58f8d98825","tid":1847723,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:35:11.000Z","msg":"尋日講咗，畀人當我天方夜譚，過咗半年都未學精。政府好快會再立緊急法！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1845715/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1845715/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"eb0e8490bafced18dd0ea50b847c5c53ad75bf3b","tid":1847723,"uid":21299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T08:03:43.000Z","msg":"用軍營做隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}